== Conferences == Numerous types of diversity training conferences exist currently throughout the world.<ref>{{cite web|title=World Experts Convene For Landmark Diversity Conference.}}</ref>{{failed verification|date=October 2016}} They have become an essential tool that a company now seeks for their employees. While most trainings are the same, some differ based on the type of sector and work the company does. Businesses look into diversity within the workplace but also within consumers while educators use diversity training as a way to learn adequate communication among students and parents.<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Lappin|first1=G|title=Diversity Training, Educational Equity, and Teacher Preparation Programs: The Promise of Multiculturalism| journal=International Journal of the Humanities|volume=5|issue=2|pages=109–113|url =http://ijh.cgpublisher.com/product/pub.26/prod.1005}}</ref> Most training is done through companies that specialize in the matter and certify those who conduct the conference.{{citation needed|date=October 2016}}
